&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the Role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are seeking an exceptional Executive Assistant who will provide a wide range of administrative, functional and operational support to the CEO. This is a highly visible, fast-paced role for someone who is proactive, organized, and thrives in a busy environment. You will play a critical role in maximizing the CEO&#39;s effectiveness by managing priorities, anticipating needs, and ensuring seamless day-to-day operations.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The ideal candidate is resourceful, detail-oriented, highly discreet, and comfortable juggling multiple priorities while maintaining exceptional standards of professionalism.&lt;/p&gt;
