&lt;li&gt;Coordinate board meetings, investor meetings, executive leadership offsites, and company events.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Track key initiatives and deadlines, ensuring projects move forward and stakeholders remain accountable.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Handle confidential information with the highest level of discretion and professionalism.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist with expense reporting, document management, and administrative processes.&lt;/li&gt;
